cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.DB, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the OAI-ORE framework, which is primarily concerned with digital libraries and the integration of their content with the Web architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries). The paper also mentions interoperability efforts and specifications, which suggest categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DB (Databases). The mention of eScience and eScholarship also suggests categories such as cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
